description:
Original Sountrack of Cities Skylines the Go Nuts Doughnuts. The Cities: Skylines Soundtrack was composed by Jonne Valtonen and Jani Laaksonen. 

Cities: Skylines by Colossal Order was published by Paradox Interactive on 10 March 2015.
